{"tid":400013,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"自煮清湯牛肋條","createTime":"2017-09-14T12:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T12:34:36.000Z","uid":18948,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f45e70f834b714a104b3caea9dfa26761dfc76b","tid":400013,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"首先有牛肋條，切到三四吋長，記住煮完會縮細，同埋建議買美國，巴西食得出冇咁好食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/g81k7tgzd/IMG_0670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fg81k7tgzd%2FIMG_0670.jpg&h=9537f315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住用牛脂肪開鑊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/tdh2dxaux/IMG_0671.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Ftdh2dxaux%2FIMG_0671.jpg&h=7abce655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加鹽煎香牛肋肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/gv52b3395/IMG_0672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fgv52b3395%2FIMG_0672.jpg&h=92727453&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f29ac2a910e9e8b9846efa6792156710bc00723","tid":400013,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"直到邊位少少焦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/wpjykyrzt/IMG_0674.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fwpjykyrzt%2FIMG_0674.jpg&h=4c3e019c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用煎牛啲油喺小煲內煎香薑片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/5b08j1u7t/IMG_0675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2F5b08j1u7t%2FIMG_0675.jpg&h=0d9f86da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加入清雞湯(唔鐘意用味精嘅師兄 bye bye )<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/dtea14q49/IMG_0676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fdtea14q49%2FIMG_0676.jpg&h=dec76d41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25b7b5f25ab9f355b6d6125276c701c81dca3cea","tid":400013,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d046d151d93a07c645876a975fbc9b33305f90","tid":400013,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:24:15.000Z","msg":"加入牛肋肉，再加適量黑椒碎，加水直到牛肋條被湯蓋住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/xdst3wqpl/IMG_0677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fxdst3wqpl%2FIMG_0677.jpg&h=9d68feb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中小火滾起 10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/xpa9go75l/IMG_0678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fxpa9go75l%2FIMG_0678.jpg&h=d8077a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斜刀切好大根/白蘿蔔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/oy38menuh/IMG_0685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Foy38menuh%2FIMG_0685.jpg&h=787dbf3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大根放入湯中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/6owgs3iux/IMG_0687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2F6owgs3iux%2FIMG_0687.jpg&h=b15879ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將肉放面，加水至湯高於材料，中火滾起20分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/914gpovg9/IMG_0688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2F914gpovg9%2FIMG_0688.jpg&h=1ed74fe7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e980e54f8756e78bc3ea72c04fbe62f2d209db7e","tid":400013,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9e88222e826bf4cba5acf4110cdfcdaea01ae2","tid":400013,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89eaf40f40a1fcc0b7270b3d76c3be69cebff428","tid":400013,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:26:28.000Z","msg":"關火等待最少1小時，食前1小時先去油，小火加熱滾起約5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s26.postimg.org/p36zw2v5l/IMG_0697.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fp36zw2v5l%2FIMG_0697.jpg&d=1rkYds7J6voarvIERUwuv54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f2b4c7a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s26.postimg.org/p36zw2v5l/IMG_0697.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n食得!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/wunpumzax/IMG_0700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fwunpumzax%2FIMG_0700.jpg&h=7c0e1538&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8f061f56811aacc2b12263f69ed00ffe9c9064f","tid":400013,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"屌你正啊喂"},{"pid":"68be69b3da8d3df8e5d34324783b4083728eff29","tid":400013,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"呢個係超簡單做法<br />\n<br />\n連油都唔使，一味餸有肉有菜<br />\n<br />\n我最後連都無落額外鹽<br />\n<br />\n如果對味精雞湯有意見用水都得，但係後期調味要重手 D"},{"pid":"754e09e0ed4415cf9430d9a08f008134bd73ea67","tid":400013,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"夠味?"},{"pid":"b82fae782058ddf66a426dd206e33c43c0eb25f3","tid":400013,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夠味?</blockquote><br />\n用雞湯夠，上菜前試下唔夠可加鹽，不建議加生抽因為會令湯深色o左，但無咁濃的清湯可以連湯都飲埋"}]}